com.facebook.litho.drawable

Class DefaultComparableDrawable

  • java.lang.Object
    • Drawable
      • com.facebook.litho.drawable.ComparableDrawable
        • com.facebook.litho.drawable.ComparableDrawableWrapper
          • com.facebook.litho.drawable.DefaultComparableDrawable

  • public final class DefaultComparableDrawable
extends ComparableDrawableWrapper
    Default Comparable Drawable uses object equals to check equivalence.

    Using this is not the recommended as semantically equal drawables will not be considered equivalent because they will have different references, which could make diffing inefficient.

Extend ComparableDrawable for custom drawables (see BorderColorDrawable) or extend ComparableDrawableWrapper and implement isEquivalentTo(ComparableDrawable) if drawable cannot extend ComparableDrawable (see ComparableColorDrawable and ComparableResDrawable).
